Usage: AWAYSAVE [-]type
  Defines what to save in ScrollZ.away

  Type is any of the following : MSG, NOTICE, MASS, COLL, CDCC, DCC,
  PROT, HACK, SRVMODE, CTCP, FLOOD, INVITE, KILL, KICK, SERVER, FAKE,
  AREPLY, CHAT, NOTIFY, SENTMSG, AWAY or ALL. You can specify
  multiple types by separating them with space. You can turn it off
  by specifying NONE. If preceeded by minus such events will not be
  saved. Note that effects accumulate so if you specify only one type
  it will be added to current set.
